Behavioral data were analyzed using the signal detection theory. For each of the four conditions, I computed a hit rate in which participants answered “old” to an old probe and a false-alarm (FA) rate in which they answered “old” to a new probe. A measure of sensitivity (d’) was computed62 using the equation\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
